@NODE "Age" "Das Ich. Age - Stupid Brainstuff - Brain - Heiko Schröder"

*****************************************************************************
*                                                                           *
*   Problems, Solutions and Tips for Finalwriter 3 up to 97 / FinalCopy II  *
